nline%2C%20sparking%20debate%20after%20she%20chose%20Jude%20Bellingham%20over%20Yamal%20and%20Kylian%20Mbappe%20in%20a%20casual%20conversation.%20Another%20clip%20showed%20Garcia%20commenting%20on%20Yamal's%20ex%2C%20Nicki%20Nicole.%20The%20videos'%20timing%20and%20full%20context%20remain%20unverified.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22BARSHA%20DUTTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Even%20Google%20couldn't%20out-earn%20its%20AI%20spending%20this%20quarter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a61383054f9875261778964%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle's%20free%20cash%20flow%20went%20negative%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20AI%20bill%20is%20finally%20coming%20due.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20raised%20its%20predicted%20capital%20expenditure%20once%20again%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20signs%20of%20it%20slowing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20for%20Google's%20AI%20spending%20spree%20is%20coming%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20its%20free%20cash%20flow%20for%20the%20second%20quarter%20turned%20to%20negative%20%245.9%20billion%2C%20as%20the%20company's%20capital%20expenditures%20continue%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20the%20company%20has%20reported%20negative%20free%20cash%20flow%20in%20decades%2C%20per%20AlphaSense%2C%20a%20signal%20of%20how%20much%20money%20Google%20is%20spending%20on%20AI%20data%20centers%20and%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Meta%20had%20already%20planned%20to%20spend%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%24700%20billion%20in%20capex%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20and%20that%20number%20only%20seems%20to%20be%20ticking%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20it%20now%20expects%20to%20spend%20%24195%20billion%20to%20%24205%20billion%20in%20capex%20for%20full-year%202026%2C%20up%20from%20its%20previous%20estimate%20of%20%24180%20billion%20to%20%24190%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnat%20Ashkenazi%2C%20Google's%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20said%20the%20company%20expects%20capex%20spend%20to%20increase%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%26quot%3B%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-q2-earnings-updates-tsla-stock-elon-musk-spacex-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20negative%20cash%20flow%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20more%20than%20two%20years%2C%20as%20Elon%20Musk's%20company%20also%20ramps%20up%20spending%20on%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20question%20about%20how%20far%20these%20dollars%20actually%20stretch%20compared%20to%20a%20year%20ago.%20Some%20analysts%20reckon%20there's%20inflation%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-spending-capex-earnings-season-memory-prices-ai-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigher%20costs%20of%20memory%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20materials%2C%20which%20make%20it%20more%20expensive%20to%20build%20out%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20things%20considered%2C%20investors%20probably%20expect%20Google's%20cash%20flow%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20red%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20the%20company%20continues%20to%20report%20strong%20revenue%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-q2-2026-earnings-historic-negative-cash-flow-ai-costs-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784762434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a614fe554f9875261778ab8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-q2-2026-earnings-historic-negative-cash-flow-ai-costs-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20reports%20negative%20cash%20flow%20due%20to%20AI%20spending%2C%20raising%20capex%20forecast%20as%20infrastructure%20costs%20rise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40businessinsider.com%20(Hugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20founders%20urge%20Trump%20not%20to%20shut%20off%20Chinese%20open%20weight%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225231%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20(R)%20is%20joined%20by%20(L-R)%20U.S.%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%2C%20U.S.%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20and%20U.S.%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20as%20he%20speaks%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20during%20the%20G7%20Leaders'%20Summit%20on%20June%2017%2C%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a614b1b548c9c486b30f780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20with%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%2C%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20and%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20as%20he%20speaks%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20during%20the%20G7%20Leaders'%20Summit.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAlmost%20200%20companies%20are%20urging%20the%20Trump%20administration%20not%20to%20cut%20off%20access%20to%20Chinese%20open-weight%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20companies%20say%20cutting%20off%20access%20risks%20crippling%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20U.S.%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20newly-formed%20Little%20Tech%20Association%20sent%20letters%20to%20the%20administration%20with%20its%20appeal%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20200%20Silicon%20Valley%20companies%2C%20including%20Proton%20and%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20are%20urging%20the%20Trump%20administration%20not%20to%20cut%20off%20access%20to%20Chinese%20open-weight%20artificial%20intelligence%20models%20or%20risk%20crippling%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20U.S.%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubscriber.politicopro.com%2Farticle%2F2026%2F07%2Fstartups-launch-new-k-street-counterweight-to-big-tech-00993757%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewly-formed%20Little%20Tech%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20letters%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20and%20others%20in%20the%20administration%20with%20its%20appeal%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20coordinated%20effort%20by%20Silicon%20Valley's%20wider%20influential%20startup%20community%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20one%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20most%20closely%20watched%20AI%20debates.%20At%20issue%3A%20whether%20Washington%20should%20restrict%20access%20to%20increasingly%20powerful%20open-weight%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%2C%20AI%20models%20whose%20weights%20are%20publicly%20available%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20models%20released%20by%20Chinese%20companies%20such%20as%20Moonshot%20AI%20and%20Alibaba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerican%20leadership%20requires%20two%20things%3A%20world-leading%20American%20open-weight%20models%20and%20continued%20access%20for%20U.S.%20builders%20to%20open%20models%20already%20available%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20startup%20founders%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.politico.com%2F4a%2Fbf%2F9c4021d8404386b0a311dcccf0e5%2Flta-open-weight-ai-letter-7-22-26.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20letter%20obtained%20by%20POLITICO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20sent%20to%20Office%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Policy%20Director%20Michael%20Kratsios.%20Instead%20of%20broad%20prohibitions%2C%20they%20argue%20the%20government%20should%20adopt%20targeted%20safeguards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20warn%20that%20banning%20Americans%20from%20downloading%20Chinese%20open-weight%20models%20wouldn't%20stop%20their%20proliferation%20%E2%80%94%20but%20would%20weaken%20U.S.%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere'll%20be%20hundreds%20of%20companies%20that%20instantly%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suhail%20Doshi%2C%20founder%20of%20AI%20infrastructure%20startup%20Particle%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20association%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubscriber.politicopro.com%2Farticle%2F2026%2F07%2Fstartups-launch-new-k-street-counterweight-to-big-tech-00993757%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20POLITICO%20first%20wrote%20about%20exclusively%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20great%20for%20Anthropic.%20We're%20all%20going%20to%20have%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20Anthropic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20took%20on%20new%20urgency%20following%20reporting%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2026%2F07%2F20%2Fai-us-china-open-source-kimi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20considering%20banning%20Chinese%20AI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shortly%20after%20Moonshot%20AI%20unveiled%20its%20powerful%20Kimi%20K3%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20leads%20the%20world%20in%20AI%20innovation%2C%20and%20President%20Trump%20will%20keep%20it%20that%20way.%20The%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20innovation%20to%20widen%20the%20gap%20between%20America%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Liz%20Huston%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20West%20Wing%20Playbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20official%20granted%20anonymity%20to%20discuss%20the%20possibility%20of%20action%20against%20Chinese%20models%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20policy%20announcement%20will%20be%20announced%20directly%20by%20the%20administration.%20Any%20reporting%20until%20then%20is%20baseless%20speculation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20reports%20sparked%20panic%20across%20Silicon%20Valley's%20startup%20community%2C%20where%20many%20founders%20rely%20on%20the%20cheaper%20Chinese%20open-weight%20models%20to%20build%20products%20and%20lack%20the%20resources%20to%20spend%20heavily%20on%20usage%20credits%20from%20U.S.%20AI%20companies%20like%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI.%20Among%20their%20fears%3A%20that%20banning%20these%20models%20would%20heavily%20advantage%20a%20handful%20of%20AI%20behemoths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20sparked%20discussions%20Monday%20night%20about%20the%20matter%20among%20senior%20White%20House%20and%20Cabinet%20members%2C%20according%20to%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20granted%20anonymity%20to%20speak%20about%20private%20discussions.%20But%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20Chinese%20open-weight%20models%20was%20not%20seriously%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20administration%20officials%20have%20continued%20escalating%20their%20rhetoric%20against%20Chinese%20AI%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20said%20Tuesday%20on%20Fox%20Business'%20%26quot%3BMornings%20with%20Maria%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20administration%20would%20investigate%20whether%20Chinese%20artificial%20intelligence%20companies%20had%20improperly%20distilled%20American%20models%20to%20power%20their%20own%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20U.S.%20can%20%26quot%3Bsanction%26quot%3B%20companies%20that%20engage%20in%20intellectual%20property%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Kratsios%20said%20the%20administration%20had%20information%20that%20Moonshot%20AI%20distilled%20Anthropic's%20Fable%20model%20while%20developing%20K3%2C%20alleging%20the%20Chinese%20company%20built%20%26quot%3Ba%20sophisticated%20internal%20platform%26quot%3B%20to%20conduct%20large-scale%20distillation%20against%20American%20models%20while%20attempting%20to%20evade%20detection.%20Kratsios%20also%20alleged%20that%20Moonshot%20had%20acquired%20Nvidia%20GB300-equipped%20servers%20to%20train%20its%20models%2C%20despite%20a%20ban%20on%20their%20sale%20to%20Chinese%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKratsios%20emphasized%20that%20the%20administration%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20supports%20the%20free%20and%20fair%20development%20of%20AI%2C%20including%20a%20thriving%20competitive%20ecosystem%20that%20spans%20frontier%20models%2C%20specialized%20systems%2C%20open-source%20frameworks%2C%20and%20open-weight%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20drawing%20a%20distinction%20between%20legitimate%20model%20distillation%20and%20industrial-scale%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoonshot%20has%20not%20publicly%20addressed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fallegations.As%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallegations.As%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20%E2%80%94%20which%20maintains%20a%20list%20of%20companies%20subject%20to%20export%20controls%20and%20licensing%20restrictions%2C%20called%20the%20Entities%20List%20%E2%80%94%20had%20not%20drafted%20plans%20to%20include%20Chinese%20AI%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20the%20first%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20position%20against%20banning%20open%20weight%20models%20also%20reflects%20a%20growing%20divide%20inside%20the%20AI%20industry%2C%20with%20heavyweights%20like%20Anthropic%20increasingly%20urging%20more%20restrictions%20on%20Chinese%20AI%20developers%20over%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20startups%20arguing%20that%20bans%20would%20do%20little%20to%20help%2C%20but%20would%20put%20startups%20at%20a%20competitive%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20Tech%20Association%20Executive%20Director%20Harry%20Godfrey%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20policymakers%20should%20use%20%26quot%3Ba%20scalpel%20rather%20than%20a%20sledgehammer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20answer%20here%20would%20be%3A%20What%20is%20the%20lightest-touch%20way%20that%20doesn't%20raise%20costs%2C%20limit%20access%20or%20inhibit%20American%20innovation%20while%20still%20addressing%26quot%3B%20legitimate%20security%20concerns%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20originally%20%3C%2Fem%3Eappeared%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2026%2F07%2F22%2Fstartup-founders-urge-trump-not-to-shut-off-chinese-open-weight-ai-01008992%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eon%20POLITICO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%20is%20courtesy%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20which%20harnesses%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20company's%20newsrooms%20to%20publish%20ambitious%20scoops%2C%20investigations%2C%20interviews%2C%20opinion%20pieces%2C%20and%20analysis.%20It%20allows%20journalists%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20from%20POLITICO%2C%20Business%20Insider%2C%20WELT%2C%20BILD%2C%20Onet%2C%20and%20Fakt%20%E2%80%94%20to%20collaborate%20on%20major%20stories%20for%20an%20international%20audience%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20across%20platforms.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founders-trump-chinese-open-weight-ai-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784761673000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a614da5548c9c486b30f791%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founders-trump-chinese-open-weight-ai-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Little%20Tech%20Association%20sent%20letters%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20and%20others%20in%20the%20administration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22eng