res%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-q2-2026-earnings-gemini-closing-in-chatgpt-1-billion-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eposition%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20tech%20giant's%20stock%20closed%20down%20about%201.24%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Alphabet%20has%20done%20this.%20In%20April%202025%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-windfall-profit-investment-which-company-anthropic-stripe-databricks-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edisclosed%20a%20similar%20%248%20billion%20paper%20gain.%20%3C%2Fa%3EGoogle%20has%20no%20obligation%20to%20disclose%20exactly%20where%20those%20gains%20come%20from%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gains%20are%20almost%20certainly%20related%20to%20very%20savvy%20investments%20the%20company%20has%20made%20in%20companies%20like%20SpaceX%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Databricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-would-earn-google-111-billion-as-an-early-investor-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20early%20SpaceX%20investor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20buying%20about%207%25%20of%20the%20company%20in%202015.%20SpaceX%20also%20uses%20Google%20Cloud%20for%20its%20Starlink%20service.%20SpaceX%20is%20currently%20worth%20about%20%241.5%20trillion%20dollars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-stock-spcx-ipo-bulls-retail-traders-elon-musk-ai-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esince%20its%20IPO%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Google%20invested%20in%20SpaceX%20when%20it%20was%20worth%20only%20about%20%2412%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20133x%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepen-investment-in-ai-anthropic-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavily%20invested%20in%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20owning%20about%20a%2014%25%20stake%20in%20the%20company%20as%20of%20last%20March%2C%20according%20to%20filings%20seen%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%20The%20AI%20lab%20was%20valued%20at%20almost%20%241%20trillion%20in%20a%20massive%20%2465%20billion%20funding%20round%20in%20May.%20Some%20investors%20think%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-soared-1-2-trillion-valuation-on-secondary-markets-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealready%20worth%20%241.2%20trillion.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Google%20is%20an%20investor%20in%20Databricks%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.databricks.com%2Fcompany%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fdatabricks-raising-strategic-round-funding-188-billion-valuation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20valued%20at%20%24188%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20funding%20round%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Databricks%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20investing%20chops%20are%20certainly%20impressive.%20But%20investors%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20Google's%20own%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20hiked%20its%20capital%20expenditures%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20%24205%20billion%20this%20year%20as%20it%20races%20to%20compete%20on%20AI.%20While%20Google%20has%20strong%20advantages%20in%20distribution%20and%20chipmaking%2C%20its%20efforts%20to%20build%20a%20leading%20AI%20model%20haven't%20paid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20keeps%20delaying%20its%20next%20big%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20which%20some%20rivals%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivals-mock-google-gemini-3-5-pro-delay-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emocking%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivals-mock-google-gemini-3-5-pro-delay-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20many%20analysts%20remain%20bullish%20on%20Google's%20fundamentals.%20Its%20revenue%20jumped%20by%20almost%2025%25%20compared%20to%20last%20year%20on%20the%20back%20of%20strong%20ads%20and%20cloud%20sales%2C%20which%20are%20also%20being%20boosted%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20impressive%20quarter%20for%20Google%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Emarketer%20principal%20analyst%20Nate%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-just-made-an-extra-98-billion-on-its-investments-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784760011000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a613c6654f98752617789c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-just-made-an-extra-98-billion-on-its-investments-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20booked%20a%20huge%20paper%20gain%20from%20startup%20investments%20likely%20including%20SpaceX%20and%20Anthropic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22crollet%40insider.com%20(Charles%20Rollet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Improving%20liquidity%20helping%20robust%20growth%20in%20credit%3A%20RBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784759590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132569843%2Cimgsize-780869.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fimproving-liquidity-helping-robust-growth-in-credit-rbi%2Farticleshow%2F132569844.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20economy%20shows%20resilience%20amid%20global%20uncertainties%20and%20fragile%20geopolitics.%20Liquidity%20conditions%20have%20improved%2C%20supporting%20robust%20credit%20growth%20across%20the%20nation.%20The%20external%20sector%20remains%20steady%2C%20with%20foreign%20investment%20inflows%20strengthening%20its%20outlook.%20Rural%20and%20urban%20dema