on%20song%20plays.%20Another%20photo%20captures%20Alcaraz%20in%20a%20Spain%20jersey%20holding%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20trophy.%20The%20clips%20give%20fans%20a%20fun%20look%20at%20two%20global%20stars%20celebrating%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20success%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sumit%20Roy%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeed-and-carlos-alcaraz-share-fun-dance-moment-at-justin-biebers-2026-world-cup-afterparty%2Farticleshow%2F132568432.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeed-and-carlos-alcaraz-share-fun-dance-moment-at-justin-biebers-2026-world-cup-afterparty%2Famp_articleshow%2F132568432.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeed-and-carlos-alcaraz-share-fun-dance-moment-at-justin-biebers-2026-world-cup-afterparty%2Famp_articleshow%2F132568432.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20summer%20blew%20up%20our%20family's%20routine%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20a%20business%20system%20from%20Toyota.%20It%20helped%20curb%20the%20chaos.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20boy%20moves%20a%20sticky%20note%20that%20his%20family%20is%20using%20to%20help%20organize%20thier%20summer%20activities.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60f317548c9c486b30f243%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20her%20family%20was%20reluctant%20to%20follow%20a%20new%20method%20for%20organizing%20their%20to-do%20list%20at%20first%2C%20but%20they%20quickly%20got%20on%20board.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Laura%20Wheatman%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20really%20dislike%20how%20disrupted%20our%20regular%20routine%20is%20when%20the%20kids%20are%20home%20during%20summer%20break.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20year%2C%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20make%20the%20days%20more%20productive%20and%20meaningful%20while%20limiting%20screens.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20turned%20to%20the%20Kanban%20method%2C%20a%20business%20system%20for%20organization%2C%20to%20keep%20my%20kids%20on%20task.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20a%20summer%20Grinch.%20I%20do%20not%20thrive%20in%20warm%20weather.%20I%20do%20not%20have%20the%20funds%20for%20extravagant%20vacations.%20Perhaps%20the%20thing%20I%20like%20least%20about%20summer%20is%20that%20my%20family's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-entertain-children-weekend-bored-hot-take-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esense%20of%20routine%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20disrupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20two%20kids%2C%2010%20and%2012%2C%20are%20spending%20several%20weeks%20of%20the%20summer%20in%20day%20camp%2C%20but%20also%20have%20stretches%20where%20we%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstopped-over-scheduling-kids-summer-were-all-happier-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20commitments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20working%20from%20home%20as%20an%20independent%20journalist%20and%20also%20have%20a%20summer%20job%20at%20a%20new%20play%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flocal-teens-fill-childcare-gaps-inexpensive-budget-friendly-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebabysitter%20takes%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20kids%20while%20I'm%20at%20the%20theatre%2C%20which%20motivates%20me%20to%20keep%20the%20house%20at%20least%20a%20little%20orderly.%20But%20I%20was%20still%20struggling%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20system%20for%20keeping%20my%20home%20and%20sanity%20intact%20while%20the%20kids%20are%20home.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETurning%20to%20a%20business%20system%20gave%20me%20some%20help%2C%20and%20some%20hope%2C%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-intentionally-doing-less-with-kids-stress-free-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esummer%20we%20could%20all%20survive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223dcf3ca9-49d4-4da6-ba95-3dcc8ac8ba2f%5C%22%3EI%20came%20across%20a%20new-to-me%20method%20of%20organizing%20our%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20researching%20ways%20to%20organize%20workflow%20online%20and%20came%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkanbantool.com%2Fkanban-guide%2Fkanban-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKanban%20method%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20intrigued.%20I%20learned%20that%20kanban%20means%20%26quot%3Bsignboard%26quot%3B%20in%20Japanese%20and%20is%20a%20business%20system%20used%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toyota-europe.com%2Fabout-us%2Ftoyota-vision-and-philosophy%2Ftoyota-production-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20like%20Toyota%3C%2Fa%3E%20(where%20it%20was%20developed).%20It%20helps%20manage%20workflow%20across%20multiple%20people%20in%20multi-step%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20background%20in%20teaching%20informed%20my%20decision%20to%20use%20this%20method%20since%20it%20involves%20%26quot%3Bchunking%26quot%3B%20a%20project%20into%20smaller%20parts.%20Instead%20of%20the%20task%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20the%20house%20clean%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20are%20smaller%20actions%20like%20%26quot%3Bwipe%20countertops%26quot%3B%20that%20are%20more%20specific%20and%20manageable.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EChunking%20is%20an%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fprocrastination%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20students%20with%20ADHD%20or%20other%20barriers%20to%20learning%2C%20and%20my%20kids%20fall%20into%20that%20category.%20I%20broke%20out%20the%20Post-It%20notes%20and%20got%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e697113d-b743-48a8-95f0-26b749b16f8d%5C%22%3ESetting%20up%20the%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20learning%20about%20how%20kanban%20can%20help%20people%20maximize%20their%20productivity%2C%20I%20made%20the%20unpopular%20household%20decision%20that%20we%20would%20be%20implementing%20the%20method%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20some%20trial%20and%20error%20while%20constructing%20my%20board.%20The%20first%20version%20was%20just%20putting%20sticky%20notes%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20but%20they%20kept%20falling%20down%2C%20so%20I%20pinned%20a%20bright%20square%20of%20wrapping%20to%20the%20wall.%20The%20sticky%20notes%20stuck%20to%20the%20paper%20better%20than%20the%20wall.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20put%20a%20solid%20piece%20of%20paper%20on%20one%20side%20to%20indicate%20the%20%26quot%3Bdone%26quot%3B%20section.%20Then%2C%20I%20assigned%20colors%20to%20each%20kid%20and%20designated%20a%20third%20color%20for%20activities%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteaching-my-son-to-do-chores-independently-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanyone%20could%20do%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20that%20they%20could%20do%20together%2C%20such%20as%20putting%20away%20clean%20dishes%20or%20playing%20a%20board%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Summer%20activities%20for%20kids%20written%20out%20on%20sticky%20notes.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60f3f2ce52cb26b83927de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20she%20added%20a%20few%20fun%20activities%20to%20help%20balance%20the%20days%20for%20her%20kids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Laura%20Wheatman%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293d4a39e-02f1-4749-a06c-511723d4b1da%5C%22%3EIt's%20working%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20one%20highly%20independent%2C%20artsy%20middle%20schooler%20and%20one%20extremely%20energetic%2C%20very%20social%20elementary%20schooler%2C%20so%20I%20assigned%20them%20very%20different%20tasks%20to%20suit%20their%20own%20abilities%20and%20interests.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20older%20kid%20is%20writing%20a%20novel%2C%20so%20I%20made%20a%20sticky%20note%20for%20that%20activity.%20My%20younger%20kid%20is%20more%20into%20playing%20with%20the%20dogs%2C%20so%20I%20assigned%20that%20as%20a%20chore%20to%20him.%20I%20also%20gave%20each%20kid%20two%2020-minute%20reading%20slots.%20I'd%20like%20it%20if%20my%20kids%20saw%20free%20reading%20as%20leisure%20time%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20who%20they%20are%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20some%20fun%20tasks%20on%20the%20board%2C%20screentime%20is%20not.%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-summer-schedule-fun-chores-boring-first-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enot%20strict%20about%20screens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20all%20regulate%20with%20them%2C%20and%20I%20think%20some%20of%20the%20secret%20to%20my%20meager%20parenting%20successes%20over%20the%20years%20is%20that%20I%20allow%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20screentime%20no%20matter%20what.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20allotted%20morning%20screentime%20is%20up%2C%20I%20expect%20kids%20to%20be%20doing%20work%20from%20the%20board.%20We%20all%20take%20a%20little%20screentime%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20whether%20it's%20solo%20game%20time%20or%20a%20family%20movie%2C%20to%20decompress%20and%20escape%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20considered%20assigning%20myself%20a%20color.%20I%20thought%20having%20a%20visual%20representation%20of%20all%20the%20tasks%20I%20do%20might%20give%20the%20kids%20some%20empathy%20for%20me%20and%20might%20inspire%20them%20to%20do%20their%20own%20part%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20against%20it%20for%20now.%20If%20I%20start%20getting%20push-back%20as%20the%20summer%20tips%20into%20its%20second%20half%2C%20I'll%20reconsider.%20Who%20knows%2C%20maybe%20I'll%20find%20it%20helps%20me%20with%20productivity%20as%20well.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhile%20the%20kids%20were%20reluctant%20of%20this%20system%20at%20first%2C%20they%20got%20on%20board%20when%20they%20saw%20that%20each%20task%20took%20relatively%20little%20time%20compared%20to%20their%20expectations%2C%20and%20that%20they%20still%20had%20lots%20of%20time%20for%20their%20precious%20tablets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkanban-method-business-system-helped-organize-family-to-do-list-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784758021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60f317548c9c486b30f243%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkanban-method-business-system-helped-organize-family-to-do-list-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tried%20the%20Kanban%20method%20with%20my%20kids%20to%20make%20summer%20run%20more%20smoothly%20in%20our%20house.%20It's%20working.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Wheatman%20Hill)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20year%20after%20deadly%20jet%20crash%20at%20Bangladesh%20school%2C%20families%20demand%20answers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784757847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Face%2Fbranded_news%2F1200%2Fcpsprodpb%2Ff3d8%2Flive%2Febe69aa0-85a6-11f1-a300-4537eea2be58.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2j7jgg1z1o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20week%20marks%20one%20year%20since%20a%20military%20jet%20struck%20a%20school%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20killing%2036%2C%20most%20of%20them%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2j7jgg1z1o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blocked%20by%20censors%2C%20China's%20animal%20lovers%20take%20fight%20against%20abuse%20offline%20and%20overseas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784757823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.