cts%20that%20spending%20likely%20won't%20cool%20as%20much%20as%20Wall%20Street%20anticipates%2C%20leaving%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20bull%20thesis%20intact.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Table%20titled%20Capex%20Estimates%20compares%20GOOG%2C%20META%2C%20MSFT%2C%20and%20AMZN%20percentage%20estimates%20across%20CY26E%20and%20CY27E.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60ea3a548c9c486b30f1b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20earnings%20chart%20provided%20by%20Munster%20in%20his%20analysis%20on%20his%20web%20page.%3Cp%3EGeneMunster.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMunster%20noted%20that%20much%20of%20his%20analysis%20centers%20on%20the%20themes%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-capex-boom-meta-microsoft-amazon-alphabet-goldman-sachs-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20capex%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cloud%20computing%20in%20Q2%20tech%20earnings%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20equally%20important%20for%20investors.%20But%20while%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20sees%20Microsoft%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-stock-price-outlook-ai-trade-oracle-parallels-black-sheep-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20weakest%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20hyperscaler%20chain%2C%20even%20its%2020%25%20year-to-date%20decline%20isn't%20enough%20to%20derail%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20boom.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20narrative%20risk%20in%20the%20capex%20conversation%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmsft-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20believe%20management%20will%20guide%20investors%20to%20an%20unchanged%2026%25%20growth%20rate%20for%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Munster%20noted.%20%26quot%3BIf%20three%20of%20the%20four%20hyperscalers%20raise%20their%20outlook%2C%20I%20believe%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20narrative%20will%20remain%20intact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMunster%20says%20that%20these%20stocks%20look%20cheap%20relative%20to%20recent%20earnings.%20He%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20example%20of%20a%20company%20that%20hasn't%20grown%20as%20quickly%20as%20Wall%20Street%20anticipated%2C%20resulting%20in%20its%20valuation%20multiples%20being%20pushed%20lower%2C%20from%20trading%20at%2030x%20earnings%20projections%20last%20year%20to%2016x%202027%20estimates%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Munster's%20perspective%2C%20valuation%20compression%20is%20a%20natural%20step%20for%20these%20companies%2C%20as%20colossal%20growth%20of%20past%20quarters%20becomes%20harder%20to%20sustain.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20investors%20should%20be%20worried%2C%20and%20earnings%20could%20be%20the%20update%20the%20bulls%20need%20to%20resume%20the%20rally.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20expect%20earnings%20to%20continue%20growing%20by%20more%20than%2020%25%20annually%20for%20the%20next%20several%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20that%20proves%20true%2C%20it%20would%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20AI%20infrastructure%20stocks%20to%20continue%20working%2C%20as%20earnings%20growth%20more%20than%20offsets%20the%20decline%20in%20valuation%20multiples.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-earnings-ai-capex-hyperscalers-msft-nvda-gene-munster-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784748079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a6100ab548c9c486b30f302%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-earnings-ai-capex-hyperscalers-msft-nvda-gene-munster-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Capex%20is%20t