6-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20pushing%20to%20build%20community%20support%20for%20a%20planned%20new%20data%20center%20in%20Georgia%20in%20an%20apparent%20effort%20to%20avoid%20the%20type%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalm-beach-florida-ai-data-center-trump-mar-a-lago-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebacklash%20rising%20against%20AI%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20projects%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20maker%20on%20Wednesday%20unveiled%20its%20plans%20to%20build%20%26quot%3BProject%20Camellia%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20at%20least%20%2420%20billion%20data%20center%20campus%20in%20rural%20Effingham%20County%2C%20just%20outside%20Savannah%2C%20that%20will%20require%203.2%20gigawatts%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20that%20it%20has%20been%20meeting%20with%20state%20and%20local%20officials%2C%20community%20leaders%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20to%20gather%20feedback%20on%20the%20project%20and%20will%20hold%20a%20public%20open%20house%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20showing%20up%20early%20is%20the%20right%20way%20to%20build%20trust%2C%20with%20that%2C%20we%20are%20still%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20development%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BSignificant%20work%20remains%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20project%20phasing%2C%20design%2C%20financing%2C%20and%20operating%20model.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEffingham%20County%20Commissioner%20Jamie%20DeLoach%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20%26quot%3Basked%20the%20tough%20questions%26quot%3B%20and%20found%20that%20the%20project%20%26quot%3Buses%20minimal%20water%2C%20won't%20increase%20energy%20costs%20for%20county%20residents%2C%20will%20generate%20new%20tax%20revenue%20to%20support%20our%20schools%2C%20and%20create%20new%20opportunities%20for%20local%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20added%20it%20has%20contracted%20with%20Georgia%20Power%20to%20deliver%20electricity%20to%20the%201%2C400-acre%20campus%20in%20phases%20between%202028%20and%202032.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5fc9f6c-e19c-4860-93a6-aa938bdcf524%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20says%20water%20use%20will%20be%20'minimal%2C'%20utility%20bills%20won't%20rise%2C%20and%20schools%20get%20free%20AI%20tokens%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20announcement%2C%20OpenAI%20detailed%20a%20four-point%20pledge%20addressing%20issues%20that%20have%20fueled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-protests-ai-trade-markets-sei-be-morgan-stanley-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewidespread%20opposition%20to%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20elsewhere%2C%20including%20electricity%20costs%2C%20water%20use%2C%20and%20community%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20local%20residents%20would%20not%20see%20higher%20electricity%20bills%20because%20of%20the%20project%20and%20that%20the%20facility's%20water%20use%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bminimal%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-data-centers-are-deepening-the-water-crisis-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclosed-loop%20water%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeorgia%20families%20will%20not%20subsidize%20this%20project.%20OpenAI%20will%20pay%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20electric-service%20costs%20required%20to%20serve%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20project%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20first%20data%20centers%20designed%20to%20%26quot%3Bproactively%20reduce%20its%20power%20consumption%20before%20residential%20customers%20are%20impacted%20during%20periods%20of%20high%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20also%20said%20it%20would%20provide%20%2480%20million%20in%20community%20benefits%20over%20the%20life%20of%20the%20project%20and%20will%20make%20up%20to%20%2471%20million%20in%20credits%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-codex-micro-shortcuts-agent-work-louder-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECodex%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20AI%20coding%20tool%2C%20available%20to%20eligible%20Georgia%20college%2C%20community%20college%20and%20technical%20school%20students.%20Georgia%20students%20who%20are%20eligible%20will%20get%20%24100%20in%20Codex%20credits%20through%20their%20ChatGPT%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20independent%20firm%20will%20conduct%20an%20annual%20audit%20of%20OpenAI's%20commitments%20to%20be%20released%20to%20the%20public%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20expects%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecreate%20thousands%20of%20construction%20jobs%20and%20more%20than%201%2C000%20operational%20roles%20once%20the%20campus%20is%20fully%20built%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECompanies%20are%20racing%20to%20build%20AI%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20throughout%20the%20country%20and%20many%20communities%20are%20pushing%20back%20over%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20environmental%20and%20economic%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-popularity-us-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20acknowledged%20the%20challenge%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20not%20very%20popular%20in%20the%20US%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20centers%20are%20getting%20blamed%20for%20electricity%20price%20hikes.%20Almost%20every%20company%20that%20does%20layoffs%20is%20blaming%20AI%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20really%20is%20about%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20research%20project%20Data%20Center%20Watch%2C%20at%20least%2075%20data%20center%20proposals%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%24130%20billion%20were%20delayed%20or%20blocked%20during%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%202026%20due%20to%20local%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20May%2C%20there%20were%20at%20least%20430%20local%20Facebook%20groups%20with%20more%20than%20525%2C000%20members%20fighting%20back%20against%20AI%20data%20centers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Data%20Center%20Opposition%20Report%2C%20which%20tracks%20local%20opposition%20to%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorgia's%2012th%20Congressional%20District%20Democratic%20Committee%20has%20issued%20an%20%26quot%3Burgent%20call%20to%20action%26quot%3B%20via%20Facebook%2C%20urging%20community%20members%20to%20show%20up%20to%20Thursday's%20public%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20New%20York%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20imposing%20the%20nation's%20first%20statewide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-state-ai-data-center-moratorium-temporary-ban-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emoratorium%20on%20large-scale%20data%20centers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-effingham-georgia-data-center-project-camellia-water-use-tokens-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784745938000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60f08cce52cb26b8392798%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-effingham-georgia-data-center-project-camellia-water-use-tokens-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20latest%20data%20center%20proposal%2C%20%26quot%3BProject%20Camellia%2C%26quot%3B%20included%20pledges%20regarding%20electricity%20bills%2C%20water%20use%2C%20and%20Codex%20credits%20for%20students.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmus