tch%20has%20begun%20to%20pop%20up%20for%20preorder%20through%20select%20cellular%20providers%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20preorder%20on%20the%20Samsung%20website%20and%20don't%20elect%20trade-in%2C%20you'll%20be%20eligible%20for%20a%20%24100%20Samsung%20Instant%20Credit.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20credit%20usually%20can't%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20purchase%20of%20the%20watch%20itself%20and%20is%20instead%20best%20used%20for%20accessories.%20If%20you%20preorder%20through%20Amazon%2C%20you%20have%20the%20option%20to%20purchase%20the%20watch%20along%20with%20a%20%24100%20gift%20card%20at%20no%20extra%20cost%20(it's%20listed%20as%20a%20%24100%20deal%20on%20a%20%24799.99%20bundle).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250ad0a13-49f1-43b1-9b4c-0c5cc3df225c%5C%22%3EWhat's%20new%20in%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%20Ultra%202%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20showing%20three%20different%20screens%3A%20Trail%20Run%2C%20health%20metrics%2C%20and%20a%20general%20running%20tracker.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60f68c54f9875261778578%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Galaxy%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20boasts%20multiple%20upgraded%20features%20compared%20to%20its%20predecessor.%20All%20of%20these%20metrics%20have%20been%20reported%20by%20Samsung.%20While%20our%20team%20briefly%20interacted%20with%20the%20Ultra%202%20in%20person%2C%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20put%20it%20through%20our%20rigorous%20testing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELonger%20battery%20life%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Ultra%202%20features%20an%20800%20mAh%20battery%2C%20a%2035%25%20increase%20in%20capacity%20over%20the%20previous%20Ultra%20model.%20The%20watch%20was%20rated%20for%20up%20to%2060%20hours%20of%20use%20(AOD%20On)%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESlimmer%20design%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Despite%20the%20larger%20battery%2C%20the%20watch%20has%20an%20overall%20thinner%2C%20redesigned%20profile%20(12%25%20thinner%20compared%20to%20the%20last%20generation)%2C%20adding%20to%20its%20sleek%20ability%20to%20transition%20from%20outdoor%20exercise%20to%20everyday%20wear.%20The%20new%20bands%20are%20also%20lighter%2C%20offering%20a%20more%20breathable%20and%20comfortable%20fit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20watch%20is%20powered%20by%20the%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%20Wear%20Elite%20(replacing%20Exynos)%2C%20enhancing%20power%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20GPS%20tracking.%20This%20display%20is%20also%20ultra-bright%2C%20with%20an%20unparalleled%205%2C000%20nits%20(maximum).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrail%20Run%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20new%20Trail%20Run%20feature%20can%20help%20outdoor%20adventurers%2C%20including%20ultra%20runners%2C%20better%20track%20their%20progress%2C%20terrain%2C%20and%20elevation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENutrition%20Alert%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20new%20addition%20to%20the%20sweat%20loss%20feature%20can%20help%20estimate%20hydration%20needs%20throughout%20a%20workout.%20The%20guidance%20considers%20sweat%20loss%20and%20body%20weight%20to%20estimate%20necessary%20rehydration%20amounts%20and%20frequency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiving%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20innovative%20and%20unique%20new%20Ultra%20Watch%202%20feature%20is%20the%20Diving%20app%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20later%20this%20year.%20The%20feature%20was%20developed%20with%20the%20Mares%20diving%20brand%20to%20track%20real-time%20diving%20data%2C%20including%20depth%2C%20time%2C%20water%20temperature%2C%20ascent%2Fdescent%20speed%2C%20and%20safe%20dive%20limits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Both%20the%20Galaxy%20Ultra%202%20and%20the%20new%20Galaxy%20Watch%209%20include%20AI-powered%20health%20insights%2C%20including%20a%20sleep%20apnea%20feature%2C%20vital%20monitoring%2C%20heart%20health%20score%2C%20daily%20cardio%20load%20training%20guidance%2C%20fitness%20index%2C%20and%20hearing%20alerts%20and%20reports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20takeaway%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I'm%20a%20runner%20and%20fitness%20tech%20enthusiast%20(Garmin%20is%20my%20current%20go-to)%2C%20and%20battery%20life%20and%20GPS%20tracking%20capabilities%20are%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game.%20None%20of%20the%20flashy%20extra%20perks%20matter%20without%20these%20fundamental%20features%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20embarking%20on%20lengthy%20and%20potentially%20remote%20outdoor%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%2C%20I'm%20intrigued%20by%20the%20advancements%20in%20battery%20life%2C%20which%20would%20push%20the%20Galaxy%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20ahead%20of%20the%20newest%20Apple%20Watch%20Ultra%203.%20That%20said%2C%20I'm%20still%20curious%20how%20this%20will%20stack%20up%20against%20some%20of%20Garmin's%20advanced%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dive%20function%20is%20also%20pretty%20cool%20and%20definitely%20unique.%20Depending%20on%20how%20it%20compares%20to%20Apple's%20diving%20features%2C%20it%20could%20be%20the%20smartwatch%20of%20choice%20for%20serious%20divers.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20how%20helpful%20this%20will%20be%20for%20the%20everyday%20user%2C%20or%20even%20triathletes%20(where%20the%20swimming%20portion%20of%20a%20race%20is%20horizontal%20and%20doesn't%20involve%20diving)%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20fun%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%20Ultra%202%20bands%20are%20displayed%20on%20a%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60db2b548c9c486b30f083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3