rolled%20out%20three%20faster%2C%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-35-pro-flash-cyber-lite-speed-token-price-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecost-effective%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20delay%20its%20next%20frontier%20model%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-3-5-pro-july-release-tokens-ai-agents-model-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%203.5%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20this%20week's%20launches%20will%20be%20enough%20to%20keep%20users%20and%20investors%20happy%20in%20the%20interim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Google's%20competitors%20are%20using%20the%20opportunity%20to%20land%20a%20few%20jabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandr%20Wang%2C%20Meta's%20chief%20AI%20officer%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20%26quot%3Bgemini%20who%3F%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20a%20leaderboard%20that%20ranked%20Meta's%20Spark%20model%20above%20one%20launched%20by%20Google%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThibault%20Sottiaux%2C%20a%20member%20of%20technical%20staff%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20also%20took%20an%20apparent%20jab%20at%20the%20search%20giant.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Google's%20Logan%20Kilpatrick%20announced%20that%20pre-training%20on%20Gemini%204%20%E2%80%94%20the%20next%20big%20milestone%20model%20%E2%80%94%20had%20begun.%20%26quot%3BHope%20it%20finishes%20one%20day%20too!%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fthsottiaux%2Fstatus%2F2079647758869475531%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESottiaux%20replied%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220d7b3cc-dcb2-420c-94f5-48059f41e14b%5C%22%3E'Too%20early%20to%20count%20anyone%20out'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20delay%20is%20particularly%20glaring%20because%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20have%20rolled%20out%20new%20top-tier%20models%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20The%20pushback%20of%20Gemini%203.5%20Pro%20has%20%26quot%3Bshifted%20perception%20from%20leading%20edge%20to%20trailing%20edge%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Josh%20Beck%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Raymond%20James%2C%20in%20a%20note%20this%20week.%20He%20said%20he%20saw%20this%20as%20a%20byproduct%20of%20the%20fast%20pace%20of%20change%20among%20the%20labs%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Google's%20business%20has%20been%20humming%20along%20nicely%20in%20recent%20quarters%2C%20with%20strong%20momentum%20across%20Search%2C%20YouTube%2C%20Cloud%2C%20and%20other%20areas%20benefiting%20from%20Google's%20AI%20advancements.%20Google%20is%20also%20betting%20that%20faster%2C%20more%20cost-effective%20models%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-cost-tokens-gemini-flash-openai-anthropic-gemini-search-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emay%20be%20a%20winning%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20time%20when%20token%20costs%20are%20racking%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22in%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Egemini%20who%3F%20%F0%9F%8F%8E%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%92%A8%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5ANVqtBDkE%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5ANVqtBDkE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Alexandr%20Wang%20(%40alexandr_wang)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Falexandr_wang%2Fstatus%2F2079707749412483104%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2021%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20focus%20on%20more%20efficient%20models%20has%20received%20praise%20from%20some%20users.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20gets%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20on%20here%20for%20falling%20behind%20on%20agentic%20coding%2C%20but%20Gemini%203.5%20Flash%20has%20long%20been%20my%20daily%20driver%20for%20agentic%20document%20extraction%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20highest-value%20use-cases%20for%20LLMs%20IMO%2C%26quot%3B%20Kyle%20Walker%2C%20founder%20of%20Clearfork%20Intelligence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkyle_e_walker%2Fstatus%2F2079604343758606607%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Google%20may%20need%20to%20address%20this%20trade-off%20between%20efficiency%20and%20power%20when%20it%20announces%20Q2%20earnings%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%20Analysts%20are%20likely%20to%20raise%20the%20topic%20of%203.5%20Pro%20and%20its%20release%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20Gemini%2C%20probably%20more%20than%20I%20should%20but%20them%20hyping%204%20before%20even%20delivering%203.5%20Pro%20is%20a%20lil%20weird%2C%26quot%3B%20Anshel%20Sag%2C%20analyst%20at%20Moor%20Insights%20%26amp%3B%20Strategy%2C%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fanshelsag%2Fstatus%2F2079869147136110641%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESag%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20felt%20that%20Google%20hyping%20up%20Gemini%204%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Badmission%20they%20already%20have%20something%20better.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bfeverish%20pace%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%20right%20now%20doesn't%20necessarily%20yield%20meaningful%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20feel%20like%20Google%20is%20a%20much%20bigger%20company%20and%20moves%20a%20bit%20differently%20from%20its%20competitors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20way%20too%20early%20to%20count%20anyone%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20something%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehlangley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%