it-turns-green-every-20000-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F132563634.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Monday.com%20plans%2020%25%20layoffs%20citing%20an%20'AI-driven%20growth%20strategy.'%20Read%20the%20co-CEO's%20memo%20to%20employees.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20logo%20for%20Monday.com%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60e8f854f9875261778489%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMonday.com%20cited%20its%20%26quot%3BAI-driven%20growth%20strategy%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20layoff%20plans.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Thomas%20Fuller%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMonday.com%20plans%20to%20cut%2020%25%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20securities%20filing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20project%20management%20platform%20cited%20its%20%26quot%3BAI-driven%20growth%20strategy%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20disclosure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20has%20slumped%20in%20the%20last%20year%20as%20fears%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-apocalypse-salesforce-microsoft-executives-not-worried-2026-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eof%20a%20%26quot%3BSaaSpocalypse%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20cuts%20are%20coming%20for%20Monday.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcmo-monday-assess-people-product-position-new-roles-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenterprise%20software%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20plans%20to%20cut%2020%25%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Form%206-K%20it%20filed.%20The%20layoffs%20are%20meant%20to%20align%20the%20company%20with%20its%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20focus%20on%20the%20AI%20Work%20Platform%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20disclosure%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonday.com%20joins%20the%20growing%20group%20of%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eciting%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20announcing%20layoffs%2C%20like%20Snap%20and%20Block.%20Monday.com%20said%20that%20it%20was%20pursuing%20an%20%26quot%3BAI-driven%20growth%20strategy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20entered%20a%20new%20era%20where%20AI%20is%20transforming%20the%20role%20of%20software%2C%20creating%20the%20greatest%20opportunity%20our%20industry%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Monday.com%20cofounder%20and%20co-CEO%20Eran%20Zinman%20said%20in%20a%20message%20to%20employees%2C%20which%20he%20published%20to%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20new%20market%20to%20capture.%20Without%20a%20fundamental%20change%20in%20how%20we%20operate%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20and%20win%20that%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20mean%20Monday.com%20is%20becoming%20flatter%20with%20more%20autonomous%20teams%2C%20Zinman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20whether%20the%20layoffs%20were%20driven%20by%20AI%20improvements%2C%20the%20co-CEO%20wrote%20that%20the%20decision%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20made%20to%20reduce%20costs%20or%20replace%20people%20with%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Monday.com%20plans%20to%20cut%2020%25%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20it%20also%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20continue%20hiring%20in%20areas%20of%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20exactly%20how%20many%20workers%20will%20be%20affected.%20In%20its%202025%20annual%20report%2C%20Monday.com%20said%20that%20it%20had%203%2C155%20employees.%20Monday.com%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20rose%20throughout%20the%20morning%2C%20though%20it%20has%20since%20ticked%20back%20down.%20The%20stock%20has%20slumped%20roughly%2075%25%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonday.com%20provides%20project%20management%20software%20to%20enterprises.%20This%20category%20is%20the%20target%20of%20growing%20%26quot%3BSaaSpocalypse%26quot%3B%20worries.%20Investors%20and%20analysts%20fret%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-selloff-reactions-jensen-huang-steven-sinofsky-arm-ceo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20and%20vibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20weaken%20companies'%20reliance%20on%20these%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff0f0d1a-0a8f-4b93-8be8-adf6f3ea661e%5C%22%3ERead%20the%20Monday.com%20co-CEO's%20full%20memo%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EHi%20everyone%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EOver%20the%20past%20nine%20months%2C%20we%20have%20shifted%20our%20core%20vision%20moving%20from%20managing%20work%20to%20doing%20the%20work%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20with%20people%20and%20AI%20agents%20working%20together%20in%20one%20workspace.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20has%20required%20us%20to%20change%20our%20product%2C%20our%20strategy%2C%20and%20how%20we%20serve%20our%20customers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EBut%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20changing%20our%20strategy%20and%20product%20is%20not%20enough.%20The%20organization%20we%20built%20for%20our%20previous%20chapter%20is%20not%20the%20organization%20that%20fits%20the%20new%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20we%20are%20announcing%20the%20very%20difficult%20decision%20to%20reduce%20our%20global%20workforce%20by%20~20%25%2C%20affecting%20around%20620%20people.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20painful%20decision%20we%20have%20made%20since%20founding%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Emonday.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20-%20yet%20we%20are%20certain%20it%20is%20the%20right%20one.%20We%20made%20it.%20We%20own%20it.%20And%20we%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20people%20leaving%20are%20talented%20colleagues%20and%20friends.%20They%20helped%20build%20this%20company%2C%20support%20our%20customers%2C%20and%20create%20a%20culture%20we%20are%20deeply%20proud%20of.%20We%20are%20incredibly%20grateful%20to%20them%2C%20and%20we%20know%20that%20nothing%20we%20say%20can%20lessen%20the%20impact%20this%20will%20have%20on%20them%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20not%20making%20this%20change%20to%20protect%20what%20we%20have.%20We%20are%20making%20it%20to%20go%20all%20in%20on%20what%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Emonday.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20can%20become.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227cdeb56-e031-4051-a156-61b508fd2659%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWhy%20are%20we%20making%20this%20change%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20entered%20a%20new%20era%20where%20AI%20is%20transforming%20the%20role%20of%20software%2C%20creating%20the%20greatest%20opportunity%20our%20industry%20has%20ever%20seen.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20have%20a%20new%20market%20to%20capture.%20Without%20a%20fundamental%20change%20in%20how%20we%20operate%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20and%20win%20that%20market.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20fully%20realize%20this%20opportunity%2C%20and%20ensure%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emonday.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20positioned%20to%20lead%20in%20this%20landscape%2C%20we%20need%20to%20move%20faster%2C%20execute%20more%20decisively%2C%20take%20on%20new%20challenges%2C%20respond%20quickly%20to%20market%20changes%2C%20and%20empower%20people%20in%20the%20company%20to%20create%20greater%20impact.%20Some%20of%20the%20things%20we%20are%20changing%20in%20monday%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EA%20flatter%20organization%20-%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20reducing%20management%20layers%2C%20creating%20more%20empowered%20teams%2C%20and%20enabling%20faster%20decision-making.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMore%20autonomous%20teams%20-%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20moving%20from%20teams%20with%20many%20dependencies%20to%20smaller%20groups%20with%20broader%20ownership%20and%20greater%20authority%20to%20execute.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EA%20new%20go-to-market%20model%20-%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20new%20offering%20is%20opening%20a%20new%20market%2C%20and%20that%20market%20requires%20us%20to%20work%20differently.%20New%20and%20existing%20customers%20increasingly%20expect%20deeper%20implementation%20support%20as%20they%20adopt%20AI.%20We%20will%20work%20more%20closely%20with%20customers%2C%20increase%20our%20on-site%20presence%2C%20create%20new%20roles%2C%20and%20adapt%20many%20existing%20ones.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EImproving%20margins%20was%20not%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20decision.%20We%20intend%20to%20reinvest%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20savings%20in%20our%20people%2C%20our%20products%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20future%20growth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239e2dea0-8e5c-411c-b028-e2ee2a10633d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20the%20people%20leaving%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Emonday.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThank%20you.%20Thank%20you%20for%20all%20your%20hard%20work%2C%20for%20the%20significant%20impact%20you%20have%20made%2C%20for%20caring%20so%20deeply%20about%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Emonday.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20for%20always%20being%20willing%20to%20help%20and%20lend%20a%20hand.%20We%20know%20this%20is%20part%20of%20our%20culture%2C%20and%20it%20is%20something%20we%20consistently%20hear%20from%20everyone%20who%20interacts%20with%20people%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmonday.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Emonday.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20be%20very%20clear%3A%20this%20decision%20is%20not%20a%20reflection%20of%20your%20performance%2C%20your%20contribution%2C%20or%20your%20value.%20It%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20management%20decision%20about%20how%20to%20structure%20the%20company%20for%20its%20next%20chapter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20committed%20to%20supporting%20you%20through%20this%20transition%20with%20care%2C%20respect%2C%20and%20meaningful%20assistance.%20We%20will%20do%20everything%20we%20reasonably%20can%20to%20help%20you%20find%20your%20next%20opportunity%2C%20and%20we%20will%20provide%20you%20with%20a%20generous%20support%20package.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20companies%20that%20are%20hiring%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20we%20recommend%20these%20people%20wholeheartedly.%20They%20are%20exceptional%20professionals%20and%20teammates%2C%20and%20we%20will%20help%20connect%20them%20with%20organizations%20looking%20for%20outstanding%20talent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df0868b9-24b6-4263-956b-681385d1e63f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20the%20people%20staying%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20be%20part%20of%20such%20a%20significant%20change%20or%20to%20see%20colleagues%20and%20friends%20leave%20so%20quickly.%20We%20understand%20how%20difficult%20this%20will%20be.%20We%20also%20owe%20you%20clarity%20about%20what%20this%20change%20means.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20change%20is%20not%20about%20asking%20fewer%20people%20to%20do%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20work.%20We%20are%20making%20real%20choices%20about%20what%20we%20will%20stop%20doing.%20We%20will%20simplify%20how%20we%20work%2C%20remove%20unnecessary%20friction%2C%20and%20give%20teams%20more%20authority%20to%20make%20decisions.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20company%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20this%20change%20will%20have%20clearer%20priorities%2C%20fewer%20layers%2C%20faster%20decisions%2C%20and%20greater%20ownership.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf5dd126-19d5-4984-9f6f-3cab1526f6ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20deeply%20confident%20about%20our%20future%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20path%20is%20very%20clear%20to%20us.%20This%20is%20a%20change%20we%20have%20chosen%20to%20make%2C%20and%20we%20are%20taking%20full%20responsibility%20for%20it.%20We%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20significant%20opportunity%20in%20software%2C%20driven%20by%20such%20exciting%20technology.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ENothing%20gives%20us%20more%20confidence%20than%20seeing%20how%20new%20and%20existing%20customers%20are%20responding%20to%20our%20new%20offering%2C%20and%20seeing%20adoption%20of%20our%20AI%20products%20accelerate.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EEvery%20week%2C%20we%20see%20more%20evidence%20that%20our%20strategy%20is%20the%20right%20one.%20Customers%20are%20embracing%20our%20new%20vision%2C%20adoption%20of%20our%20AI%20capabilities%20continues%20to%20accelerate%2C%20and%20our%20confidence%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20momentum%20is%20strong%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20we%20are%20on%20the%20right%20path%20to%20success%20on%20a%20massive%20market%20opportunity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20ease%20the%20uncertainty%20around%20this%20we%20will%20send%20all%20employees%20an%20email%20message%20within%20the%20next%20hour%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20personal%20call%20from%20one%20of%20your%20managers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20all%20managers%20-%20we%20know%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20process%20this%20personally%2C%20even%20as%20you%20continue%20to%20lead%20your%20teams.%20We%20have%20every%20confidence%20in%20your%20leadership%20and%20know%20you'll%20approach%20these%20conversations%20with%20the%20care%2C%20clarity%2C%20and%20respect%20that%20define%20our%20culture.%20Thank%20you%20for%20being%20there%20for%20your%20people%20during%20this%20transition.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThank%20you%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ERoy%20%26amp%3B%20Eran%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDuring%20the%20change%20process%2C%20we%20received%20a%20few%20questions%20we'd%20like%20to%20clarify%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20the%20reason%20we%20are%20doing%20this%20reduction%20is%20to%20improve%20margins%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20No.%20Improving%20margins%20was%20not%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20decision.%20We%20intend%20to%20reinvest%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20savings%20in%20our%20talent%2C%20our%20products%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20future%20growth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20we%20plan%20more%20reductions%20in%20the%20future%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20designed%20this%20change%20to%20create%20the%20organization%20we%20believe%20we%20need%20for%20our%20next%20chapter.%20We%20are%20not%20planning%20any%20further%20workforce%20reductions.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20this%20reduction%20driven%20by%20AI%20improvements%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENo.%20While%20we%20are%20seeing%20significant%20value%20from%20AI%20internally%2C%20this%20decision%20was%20not%20made%20to%20reduce%20costs%20or%20replace%20people%20with%20AI.%20We%20see%20internal%20AI%20adoption%20as%20an%20accelerator%20of%20our%20growth.%20This%20change%20was%20made%20to%20adapt%20the%20company%20to%20our%20new%20vision.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20people%20expected%20to%20work%20harder%20now%20that%20we%20have%20less%20people%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENot%20harder%20-%20better.%20To%20give%20one%20example%2C%20we%20had%20many%20situations%20where%20work%20that%20could%20have%20been%20done%20in%20a%20few%20days%20took%20many%20months%20with%20multiple%20meetings%20and%20endless%20friction.%20This%20wasn't%20people's%20fault%20and%20everyone%20was%20frustrated%20by%20this.%20Our%20new%20org%20changes%20ownership%20to%20allow%20people%20to%20make%20decisions%20and%20move%20fast.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EYou're%20talking%20about%20the%20new%20AI%20products%2C%20what%20about%20our%20existing%20market%20and%20customers%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20lucky%20to%20have%20amazing%20customers%20that%20love%20our%20product%20and%20actually%20use%20these%20words%20to%20describe%20it.%20We%20need%20to%20be%20there%20for%20them%20with%20our%20new%20vision%20of%20doing%20the%20work%20with%20AI%20and%20not%20just%20managing%20it.%20They%20are%20also%20undergoing%20change%20and%20we%20will%20invest%20heavily%20to%20help%20them%20-%20they%20are%20our%20biggest%20asset.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmonday-com-layoffs-ai-growth-strategy-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784740045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a6