0leave%20me%20wanting%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20checking%20out%20these%20tourist%20hot%20spots%2C%20here%20are%20four%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-vs-osaka-from-someone-who-lived-both-japanese-cities-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplaces%20in%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20always%20recommend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMiyajima's%20architecture%20and%20views%20are%20worth%20the%20trip%20alone.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Itsukushima%20Shinto%20Shrine%20peaking%20through%20the%20water%20in%20Miyajima%2C%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f8789ce52cb26b8391cc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20O'Keefe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECrowds%20typically%20flock%20to%20Kyoto%20for%20its%20historic%20streetscapes%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20similarly%20exquisite%20architecture%20in%20quieter%20places%20like%20Miyajima%2C%20an%20island%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Hiroshima.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiyajima's%20charming%20streets%20feel%20frozen%20in%20time%2C%20but%20the%20ocean%2C%20mountains%2C%20and%20sacred%20free-roaming%20deer%20make%20it%20feel%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETidal%20changes%20create%20a%20magical%20backdrop%20for%20some%20of%20my%20favorite%20sites%20in%20Miyajima%2C%20including%20the%20Itsukushima%20Shinto%20Shrine%2C%20which%20features%20a%20striking%20red%20torii%20gate%20that%20looks%20like%20it's%20floating%20in%20the%20sea%20during%20high%20tide.%20It's%20also%20a%20great%20place%20to%20catch%20the%20sunset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20way%20to%20embrace%20Miyajima's%20breathtaking%20landscapes%20is%20to%20take%20the%20ropeway%20up%20Mount%20Misen%20%E2%80%94%20the%20island's%20highest%20peak%20%E2%80%94%20for%20360-degree%20views%20of%20the%20sea%2C%20temples%2C%20and%20hiking%20trails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20scenery%2C%20Miyajima%20also%20o