0as%20loudly%20as%20I%20wanted%20without%20bothering%20my%20neighbors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20my%20train%20tickets%20included%20meals%2C%20I%20was%20glad%20I%20brought%20my%20own%20snacks%20for%20the%20in-between%20times.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holds%20trail%20mix%20on%20the%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d7f8841af0d00193f0dc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20many%20of%20my%20meals%20on%20the%20train%20were%20decent%2C%20but%20there%20were%20times%2C%20like%20when%20I%20tried%20and%20disliked%20a%20salmon%20dish%2C%20that%20I%20was%20thankful%20for%20this%20bag%20of%20trail%20mix%20with%20my%20favorite%20ingredient%2C%20coconut%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20missed%20a%20few%20key%20things%20when%20packing.%20While%20I'm%20glad%20I%20brought%20a%20water%20bottle%2C%20I%20wish%20I'd%20brought%20a%20smaller%20one%20that%20would%20fit%20in%20Amtrak's%20cupholders.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20authors%20water%20bottle%20is%20seen%20next%20to%20a%20cup%20holder%20that's%20too%20small%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616d7f8841af0d00193f0dcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amtrak%20attendant%20brought%20me%20disposable%20water%20bottles%20every%20few%20hours%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20glad%20I%20brought%20my%20own%20pre-filled%20water%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20bottle%20was%20too%20wide%20for%20the%20provided%20cupholders%2C%20which%20were%20just%20big%20enough%20for%2012-ounce%20bottles.%20So%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20brought%20a%20smaller%20reusable%20water%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20thing%20I%20missed%20on%20this%20trip%20was%20motion%20sickness%20medication.%20Both%20train%20rides%20felt%20as%20bumpy%20as%20a%20flight%20when%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20is%20on.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223550%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close-up%20of%20unrecognizable%20aged%20man%20in%20casual%20shirt%20holding%20bottle%20of%20water%20and%20taking%20dramamine%20pill%20in%20bus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616ddca741af0d00193f2a11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222662%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Eshironosov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20this%20would%20only%20be%20temporary%2C%20but%20the%20whole%20ride%20felt%20shaky.%20I%20ended%20up%20feeling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmotion-sickness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotion%20sickness%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20both%20trips%20and%20kicking%20myself%20for%20not%20bringing%20any%20remedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20my%20way%20home%2C%20I%20stayed%20in%20a%20bedroom%20with%20a%20private%20shower.%20I%20would%20have%20used%20it%2C%20but%20I%20forgot%20my%20flip-flops%20to%20keep%20my%20feet%20safe%20from%20germs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20Amtrack%20shower%20floor%20is%20green%20with%20brown%20marks%20Right%3A%20A%20pair%20of%20gray%20flipflops%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F617830235d1dca0019a10dc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20planned%20on%20showering%20during%20my%2030-hour%20ride%20home%20from%20Miami%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20had%20forgotten%20my%20flip-flops.%20I%20usually%20wear%20them%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskin-diseases-you-can-get-at-the-gym-ringworm-warts-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20showers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20it's%20pretty%20easy%20to%20pick%20up%20germs%20from%20places%20where%20many%20people%20have%20walked%20barefoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20there%20weren't%20many%20visible%20outlets%20in%20the%20rooms%2C%20I%20wished%20I%20had%20packed%20a%20couple%20of%20outlet%20splitters%20to%20charge%20more%20than%20a%20few%20devices%20at%20a%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22left%3A%20outlets%20on%20the%20train%20right%3A%20two%20outlet%20splitters%20stacked%20on%20top%20of%20eachother%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F617831f55d1dca0019a10e9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20only%20saw%20a%20couple%20of%20sets%20of%20outlets%20in%20the%20rooms.%20I%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20electronics%20on%20this%20trip%3A%20two%20cameras%2C%20one%20laptop%2C%20one%20Nintendo%20Switch%2C%20one%20phone%2C%20and%20one%20pair%20of%20Bluetooth%20headphones.%20With%20several%20devices%20to%20plug%20in%2C%20I%20should%20have%20brought%20an%20outlet%20splitter%20or%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20the%20same%20reason%2C%20my%20portable%20charging%20battery%20would%20have%20come%20in%20handy%20had%20I%20remembered%20to%20bring%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20outlets%20on%20the%20train%20Right%3A%20portable%20battery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61783248e100ad00181dc2c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20have%20sworn%20I%20packed%20this%2C%20so%20I%20was%20disappointed%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20usually%20bring%20my%20neck%20pillow%20when%20I%20fly%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20think%20to%20take%20it%20on%20my%20Amtrak%20trip%20since%20my%20tickets%20included%20beds.%20It%20would%20have%20made%20the%20waking%20hours%20more%20comfortable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20leans%20agains%20a%20plane%20wall%20with%20a%20blue%20neck%20pillow%20on%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F617837495d1dca0019a1100b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20neck%20pillow%20wraps%20around%20one%20and%20a%20half%20times%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20adjust%20to%20various%20long-term%20sitting%20situations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20the%20train%20bunks%20and%20blankets%20were%20much%20more%20comfortable%20than%20I%20expected%2C%20the%20pillows%20weren't%20as%20cushy%20as%20the%20ones%20I%20had%20at%20home.%20So%20I%20wish%20I'd%20brought%20my%20own.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20The%20author%20lays%20on%20the%20train%20pillow%20Right%3A%20the%20author%20lays%20on%20her%20bedroom%20pillow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61783b3fe100ad00181dc503%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bed%20on%20the%20Amtrak%20was%20firm%20and%20slightly%20cushy%20on%20top%2C%20just%20the%20way%20I%20like%20a%20bed.%20But%20when%20I%20was%20drifting%20off%20to%20sleep%20each%20night%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20my%20fluffy%2C%20dense%2C%20soft%20pillows%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpacking-for-overnight-amtrak-train-rid