el%20Kratsios%20said%20the%20White%20House%20has%20information%20showing%20Moonshot%20AI%20distilled%20Fable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20comments%20are%20an%20escalation%20as%20the%20US%20responds%20to%20viral%2C%20China-based%20open-source%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20top%20White%20House%20official%20publicly%20accused%20Moonshot%20AI%20of%20essentially%20stealing%20from%20Anthropic%2C%20intensifying%20the%20debate%20over%20China-based%20open%20source%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20information%20that%20Moonshot%20AI%20distilled%20Anthropic's%20Fable%20for%20the%20development%20of%20its%20K3%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Kratsios%2C%20director%20of%20the%20White%20House%20Office%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Policy%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20information%20that%20Moonshot%20AI%20distilled%20Anthropic%E2%80%99s%20Fable%20for%20the%20development%20of%20its%20K3%20model.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETo%20do%20this%20they%20developed%20a%20sophisticated%20internal%20platform%20to%20conduct%20large%20scale%20distillation%20against%20U.S.%20models%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20quickly%20switch%20between%20multiple%20methods%20of%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Director%20Michael%20Kratsios%20(%40mkratsios47)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmkratsios47%2Fstatus%2F2079933645888880708%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2022%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKratsios%20said%20Moonshot%20AI%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20the%20viral%20Kimi%20K3%20model%2C%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20conceal%20its%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20do%20this%20they%20developed%20a%20sophisticated%20internal%20platform%20to%20conduct%20large%20scale%20distillation%20against%20U.S.%20models%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20quickly%20switch%20between%20multiple%20methods%20of%20access%20to%20avoid%20detection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkimi-k3-ai-model-moonshot-investors-alibaba-cloud-tencent-stock-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKimi%20K3%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20most%20impressive%20open%20source%20AI%20model%20released%20thus%20far.%20Moonshot's%20model%20has%20performed%20at%20or%20above%20the%20level%20of%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI's%20leading%20frontier%20models%20in%20benchmark%20testing.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20both%20US%20companies%20spent%20billions%20developing%20those%20models.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Moonshot%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20Kimi%20K3%20freely%20available%20for%20download%20on%20local%20devices%20and%20customizable%20to%20a%20user's%20content%20when%20it%20releases%20the%20model's%20full%20weights%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdistillation-problem-ai-industry-anthropic-openai-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDistillation%20by%20itself%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20not%20wrong%2C%20a%20point%20that%20Kratsios%20stressed%20in%20his%20statement.%20AI%20labs%20themselves%20use%20the%20process%20of%20training%20a%20less%20powerful%20model%20on%20the%20output%20of%20a%20more%20powerful%20model%20before%20releasing%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegitimate%20AI%20distillation%20used%20to%20create%20smaller%2C%20more%20efficient%20models%20plays%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20this%20open%20innovation%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20large-scale%2C%20covert%20industrial%20distillation%20aimed%20at%20stealing%20proprietary%20U.S.%20technology%20and%20undermining%20American%20research%20is%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKratsios'%20statement%20comes%20after%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreasury-secretary-chinese-ai-open-source-sanctions-kimi-k3-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuggested%20that%20the%20US%20government%20may%20sanction%20Chinese%20companies%20%3C%2Fa%3Eif%20it%20is%20proven%20that%20their%20models%20were%20improperly%20trained%20through%20a%20process%20called%20distillation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House's%20words%20so%20far%20are%20notable%2C%20as%20they%20mark%20a%20rare%20instance%20in%20which%20the%20Trump%20administration%20does%20not%20find%20itself%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20Anthropic.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20previously%20imposed%20export%20controls%20to%20block%20Anthropic%20from%20releasing%20Fable%205%2C%20its%20most%20advanced%20model%2C%20and%20in%20February%20the%20Pentagon%20moved%20to%20blacklist%20the%20AI%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThanks%20%40mkratsios47%20for%20speaking%20out%20on%20this%20important%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarah%20Heck%2C%20Anthropic's%20head%20of%20public%20policy%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20quoting%20Kratsios'%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeck%20said%20Anthropic%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20the%20White%20House%20and%20Congress%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIllicit%2C%20adversarial%20distillation%20is%20IP%20theft%20and%20industrial%20espionage%20that%20supports%20adversary%20military%20and%20intelligence%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20national%20challenge%20that%20creates%20serious%20national%20security%20risks%20for%20the%20United%20States%20and%20democratic%20allies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20US%20companies%20have%20said%20that%20their%20Chinese%20competitors%20have%20abused%20the%20process%20to%20rip%20off%20their%20intellectual%20property.%20In%20February%2C%20Anthropic%20publicly%20accused%20three%20companies%2C%20including%20Moonshot%20AI%2C%20of%20using%20distillation%20attacks%20that%20violate%20its%20terms%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Anthropic%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-kimi-k3-moonshot-ai-distillation-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784738083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a60e8d154f9875261778488%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-kimi-k3-moonshot-ai-distillation-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20have%20information%20that%20Moonshot%20AI%20distilled%20Anthropic's%20Fable%20for%20the%20development%20of%20its%20K3%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20top%20White%20House%20official%20wrote%20on%20X.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Quote%20of%20the%20day%20by%20Elon%20Musk%3A%20%26quot%3BBeing%20an%20entrepreneur%20is%20like%20eating%20glass%20and%20staring%20into%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20-%20brutally%20honest%20lesson%20on%20entrepreneurship%2C%20resilience%20and%20the%20hidden%20reality%20behind%20building%20a%20business%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784738078000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132563539%2Cimgsize-14940.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fquote-of-the-day-by-elon-musk-being-an-entrepreneur-is-like-eating-glass-and-staring-into-brutally-honest-lesson-on-entrepreneurship-resilience-and-the-hidden-reality-behind-building-a-business%2Farticleshow%2F132563515.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia