.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20like%20you%2C%E2%80%99%20my%20heart%20swells%20with%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20two%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20school%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Married%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20with%20her%20parental%20home%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20she%20balances%20household%20responsibilities%20with%20teaching.%20Her%20son%2C%20now%20seven%2C%20once%20had%20clashing%20school%20timings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496803%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20let%20my%20struggles%20show%20in%20front%20of%20my%20students.%20They%20deserve%20my%20full%20attention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%E2%80%99s%20role%20extends%20beyond%20academics.%20She%20eats%20midday%20meals%20sitting%20cross-legged%20with%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20see%20me%20eating%20from%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20plate%20as%20theirs%2C%20they%20feel%20I%20am%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20seasonal%20fevers%2C%20she%20keeps%20basic%20medicines%20in%20the%20staffroom.%20%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20rice%20is%20served%20in%20the%20midday%20meal%2C%20I%20avoid%20giving%20it%20to%20sick%20children%2C%20as%20rice%20is%20believed%20to%20aggravate%20colds.%20Instead%2C%20I%20share%20my%20tiffin%20with%20them%20before%20giving%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20school%20day%20officially%20ends%20at%202%20PM%2C%20but%20the%20work%20continues%20%E2%80%94%20preparing%20lesson%20plans%2C%20completing%20paperwork%2C%20and%20visiting%20families%20whose%20children%20miss%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20true%20reward%20of%20teaching%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20teaching%20has%20never%20been%20just%20a%20job.%20It%20is%20a%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20villages%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261821%2Finspiring-uttarakhand-teacher-pandemic-village-students-lockdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20is%20as%20much%20about%20care%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20it%20is%20about%20books.%20You%20have%20to%20build%20trust%2C%20spark%20curiosity%2C%20and%20show%20children%20that%20education%20can%20change%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20pauses%2C%20then%20adds%20softly%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%20the%20classrooms%20were%20empty%2C%20and%20I%20cried.%20Today%2C%20those%20rooms%20echo%20with%20chatter%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20learning.%20That%20is%20my%20biggest%20reward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757068200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twelve%20years%20ago%2C%20Sangeeta%20Maurya%20cried%20at%20her%20posting%20in%20Raebareli%20when%20only%2030%20of%20130%20students%20turned%20up.%20Today%2C%20through%20stories%2C%20songs%2C%20and%20compassion%2C%20she%20has%20filled%20her%20classrooms%20with%20laughter%20and%20hope%20%E2%80%94%20proving%20that%20teaching%20in%20villages%20is%20more%20than%20a%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496794%2Fa-day-in-the-life-of-rural-school-teacher-raebareli-uttar-pradesh-sangeeta-maurya%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20More%20Parents%20Are%20Adding%20Millets%20%26amp%3B%20Microgreens%20to%20Their%20Kids%E2%80%99%20Lunchboxes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeature%20image%20courtesy%3A%20Sanchita%20Daswani%2F%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fgreen-organic-raw-microgreen-sprouts-ready-2452650587%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Monday%20morning%2C%20a%20seven-year-old%20opens%20his%20tiffin%20box%20in%20school.%20Inside%20are%20bright%20orange%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20small%20tub%20of%20chutney%2C%20and%20a%20sprinkling%20of%20microgreens%20shaped%20like%20bunny%20ears.%20He%20beams%20as%20his%20friends%20crowd%20around%2C%20curious.%20In%20another%20corner%2C%20his%20classmate%20strugg